Project: SNX - Secure Unix
Author.: Antonio Feitosa <@antonio_cfc>
LICENSE: GPL v2
Description:
Operation System that formed by, basically, two pieces:

(1) Unix-like Kernel
(2) Node.JS

The mission of project: Make Operation System with built-in sandboxing and only execute node.js programs.

Proposed projects:
- NACI (Node Active Command-line Interpreter) ok, it's a shell! :)
- Authentication system (to replace posix passwd shadow)
- Auth utils (login)
- syslog
and growing...

+-----------------------+
|    System services    |
+-------------+	        |
| Auth utils  | DAEMONS	|
+-------------+---------+
| Auth system |  NASH   |
+-------------+---------+
|    INIT(BSD-like)     |
+-----------------------+
|       Node.JS         |
+-----------------------+
|        KERNEL         |
+-----------------------+

